{"id":43674,"date":"2024-01-21T19:53:55","date_gmt":"2024-01-21T14:23:55","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=43674"},"modified":"2024-04-23T11:41:37","modified_gmt":"2024-04-23T06:11:37","slug":"why-qarpentri-not-carpenter-myth-vs-reality","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/dc-updates\/why-qarpentri-not-carpenter-myth-vs-reality\/","title":{"rendered":"Settling The Carpenter Vs Interior Designer Debate: Why Qarpentri And Not A Carpenter?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Your home deserves the best furniture! Here are the benefits of hiring an interior designer to help you choose wisely and live happily.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When thinking about buying furniture for your home, you may be wondering whether to hire a local carpenter or opt for a modular furniture brand. While carpenters may seem like an affordable option, there are several myths surrounding their work that may not always be true. In this blog, we will explore some of these myths and show you why opting for a modular furniture brand like <a href=\"https:\/\/qarpentri.com\/\">Qarpentri<\/a> is a better choice for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Myth: Local Carpenters Near Me Are The Best Option For Furniture&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reality:<\/strong> While local carpenters near you may seem like a convenient option, they may not always have the professional expertise or experience required for modular furniture. We at Qarpentri, on the other hand, have a team of professional designers who have studied customer pain points for over eight years through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> and added every modular unit thoughtfully after detailed research and observation. Moreover, our experts at Qarpentri did detailed research into 100 homes across cities to find the most essential sizes and features of modular furniture so we could give you home interiors that match your need and preference.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194346\/local-carpenters-vs-professional-interior-designers-of-qarpentri-is-expertise.jpg\" alt=\"Why choosing qarpentri over carpenters near me for home interiors\" class=\"wp-image-43677\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194346\/local-carpenters-vs-professional-interior-designers-of-qarpentri-is-expertise.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194346\/local-carpenters-vs-professional-interior-designers-of-qarpentri-is-expertise-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194346\/local-carpenters-vs-professional-interior-designers-of-qarpentri-is-expertise-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194346\/local-carpenters-vs-professional-interior-designers-of-qarpentri-is-expertise-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Design your dream home with branded modular furniture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"https:\/\/qarpentri.com\/collections\/wardrobes?utm_source=designcafe&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=36563\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Check out our wardrobes with lofts in stunning colours\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/01171748\/check-out-our-wardrobes-with-lofts-in-stunning-colours.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Myth: Interior Carpenters Near Me Offer The Same Quality As Qarpentri<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reality:<\/strong> While some interior carpenters may offer similar services, they may not always have the same level of expertise or quality of materials and finishes that we provide. We use high-quality plywood sourced from plantations in Kerala. These are pressure-tested and Certified DC Gold. Thus our services come with 5 years of warranty and require minimal maintenance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194413\/qarpentri-offers-higher-quality-materials-finishes-compared-to-local-carpenters.jpg\" alt=\"Qarpentri offers higher quality materials and finishes compared to the local carpenters near you.\" class=\"wp-image-43681\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194413\/qarpentri-offers-higher-quality-materials-finishes-compared-to-local-carpenters.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194413\/qarpentri-offers-higher-quality-materials-finishes-compared-to-local-carpenters-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194413\/qarpentri-offers-higher-quality-materials-finishes-compared-to-local-carpenters-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194413\/qarpentri-offers-higher-quality-materials-finishes-compared-to-local-carpenters-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Modular furniture from Qarpentri has a 5-year warranty<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Myth: Factory-Made Civil And Semi-Modular Kitchen Won\u2019t Fit In My Home<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reality:<\/strong> The Qarpentri catalogue is built to suit the <a href=\"https:\/\/qarpentri.com\/collections\/kitchen\">modular kitchen<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/qarpentri.com\/pages\/wardrobes\">wardrobe<\/a>. All the units are made-to-measure and fit the wall sizes and requirements of your home. This helps in creating the perfect modular furniture that fits your space beautifully, improves your home\u2019s functionality and helps elevate your lifestyle too. A carpenter also wants you to believe that fillers are unnecessary and waste spaces. But in reality, carpenters just leave the back of the panels and edges unfinished and hand-paint it to save cost. We use fillers as they are essential to align the edges of the units to the wall. So you get a perfect finish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194331\/custom-modular-kitchen-wardrobes-by-qarpentri-but-not-local-carpenters.jpg\" alt=\"Custom modular kitchen, wardrobes by qarpentri, not available from carpenter in bangalore\" class=\"wp-image-43675\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194331\/custom-modular-kitchen-wardrobes-by-qarpentri-but-not-local-carpenters.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194331\/custom-modular-kitchen-wardrobes-by-qarpentri-but-not-local-carpenters-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194331\/custom-modular-kitchen-wardrobes-by-qarpentri-but-not-local-carpenters-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194331\/custom-modular-kitchen-wardrobes-by-qarpentri-but-not-local-carpenters-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Qarpentri products are made-to-measure for each client<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Myth: Local Carpenters Are Cost-Effective Compared To Qarpentri<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reality:<\/strong> Local carpenters may seem like a cost-effective solution initially. But what you have to deal with is the hidden cost and the market price fluctuations of raw materials. So you end up paying unnecessary hidden costs which makes the end price way higher than what you had thought initially. But thanks to Qarpentri\u2019s factory-to-home model, all our products are built in our own factory and delivered directly to your home. So there is no room for any additional expenses or price fluctuations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194337\/local-carpenters-not-cost-effective-compare-to-qarpentri-home-interiors.jpg\" alt=\"Local carpenters are not always cost-effective compared to qarpentri\" class=\"wp-image-43676\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194337\/local-carpenters-not-cost-effective-compare-to-qarpentri-home-interiors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194337\/local-carpenters-not-cost-effective-compare-to-qarpentri-home-interiors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194337\/local-carpenters-not-cost-effective-compare-to-qarpentri-home-interiors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194337\/local-carpenters-not-cost-effective-compare-to-qarpentri-home-interiors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Say no to hidden costs with Qarpentri<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Myth: You Should Compromise On Work Quality If You Can\u2019t Wait<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reality:<\/strong> When thinking of opting for doing your home interiors, one of the crucial things is on-time delivery. All of us have the enthusiasm to enter our dream home as soon as possible. But when working with local carpenters, we have no say in the timeline. Moreover, we have to also compromise on the quality of work or finish in the worst situations. But with Qarpentri, you can rest assured that your home will be delivered in 15 days. And with all the expertise of designers and high-quality materials, there is no room for compromise when it comes to the quality of materials, finishes or designs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194353\/qarpentri-delivers-home-interiors-in-15-days-not-by-carpenter-in-bangalore.jpg\" alt=\"Qarpentri delivers home interiors in 15 days, but not by local carpenters near bangalore\" class=\"wp-image-43678\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194353\/qarpentri-delivers-home-interiors-in-15-days-not-by-carpenter-in-bangalore.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194353\/qarpentri-delivers-home-interiors-in-15-days-not-by-carpenter-in-bangalore-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194353\/qarpentri-delivers-home-interiors-in-15-days-not-by-carpenter-in-bangalore-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194353\/qarpentri-delivers-home-interiors-in-15-days-not-by-carpenter-in-bangalore-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Get your modular furniture in just 15 days<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"https:\/\/qarpentri.com\/collections\/kitchen?utm_source=designcafe&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=36538\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Can't find the right sized modular kitchen?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/01165951\/cant-find-the-right-sized-modular-kitchen.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Myth: With Branded Firms, The Delivered Products Will Not Match Your Expectations<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Reality:<\/strong> At Qarpentri, we have worked on multiple options and a wide selection of products including everything from wardrobes with multiple door options, sliding door wardrobes, functional modular kitchens, and smart storage units so that you are spoiled with choice. We also give you a free on-site consultation to help you understand what your home will look like. Moreover, you can review the 3D, made exactly to the size, before confirmation so there is no mismatch between what you see and what you get.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194406\/qarpentri-offers-3d-visuals-consultations-unlike-local-carpenters.jpg\" alt=\"Qarpentri offers customized solutions with 3d visuals consultations, not by a nearby contractors\" class=\"wp-image-43680\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194406\/qarpentri-offers-3d-visuals-consultations-unlike-local-carpenters.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194406\/qarpentri-offers-3d-visuals-consultations-unlike-local-carpenters-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194406\/qarpentri-offers-3d-visuals-consultations-unlike-local-carpenters-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/21194406\/qarpentri-offers-3d-visuals-consultations-unlike-local-carpenters-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">You always get what you are promised at Qarpentri<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In conclusion, while there are several myths surrounding the work of carpenters and branded furniture companies, opting for a modular furniture brand like Qarpentri offers several benefits, including professional expertise, high-quality materials, thoughtful designs, 5-year warranty and after-sales service, and time and cost efficiency. By choosing Qarpentri, you can ensure that your home is furnished to the highest standards and you get the best value for your money.<\/p>\n\n\n